description: Minamino Kanade is 14 years old and she is Hibiki`s childhood friend. Kanade is a excellent student, but she is not really good at sports like Hibiki. Her excellent grades and personality make her sort of a celebrity in her school. Kanade is very mature, but also quite stubborn sometimes. She dreams of being a pastry chef when she grows up, to take over her parents` pastry shop, the Lucky Spoon. She also has a strong love for cats, especially to Hummy. As Cure Rhythm, her Theme Color is both white and light pink.
name: Minamino Kanade
